Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:24.10,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an9}我在地球學到了很多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:29.32,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an9\fad(200,0)}是這個冰冷的鋼鐵星球不可能學到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:29.32,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,0)}很多溫暖的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.45,0:08:37.33,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an9\fad(200,0)}從一起戰鬥的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:37.33,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,0)}那個人的背影裡學到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.78,0:08:39.54,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an9}所以我不後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.62,0:08:43.62,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我有必須要守護的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:46.63,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an9}就算要毀滅地球也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:49.38,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算要和他戰鬥也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:53.59,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an9\fad(0,200)}所謂朋友就要保護朋友的背後
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:57.39,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(200,0)}沒錯  這是那個人…地球的朋友教會我的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:57.39,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an9\fad(200,0)}所謂朋友就要保護朋友的背後
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.87,0:09:17.62,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an9}什麼情況!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:31.17,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8}快！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.89,0:10:48.25,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an9}老師您在做什麼呢\N快點去前線佈陣吧\N將軍已經出擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:50.18,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an9}怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:51.47,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8}那  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.02,0:13:54.85,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8}出擊的頑侍突然爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.52,0:13:54.85,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\pos(370,150)\frz10}什麼  ？！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:57.35,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}莫非…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:14:00.36,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an9\fad(200,0)}他們還有同夥…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:03.65,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8}有間諜！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:05.45,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}母艦裡混進了地球的間諜!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.70,0:14:09.82,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8}出擊中止
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:11.45,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8}立刻找出那幾隻老鼠來祭旗！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.58,0:14:14.08,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8}一隻都不能放過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.79,0:14:56.87,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an9}喂  你們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:58.87,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8}那邊是總督府
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.87,0:14:58.87,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\pos(260,100)}怎麼了\N怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:03.88,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\pos(120,220)}你們去做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.63,0:15:03.88,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8}有事告訴閣下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:05.13,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼!?  找到間諜了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.27,0:15:19.89,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an9}你們…是那時的{\fscx200}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.77,0:15:19.89,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難怪覺得你們可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:23.77,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an9}沒想到竟是武士…!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:23.77,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼你們會來到宇宙!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.04,0:16:28.67,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8}是右龍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.69,0:16:51.44,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an9}受死吧!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.12,0:16:59.20,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an9}你到底在打什麼算盤？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:12.22,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8\fad(0,200)}生意？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:20.77,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8}又要賣地球嗎？ 打著這個旗號攻進這裡的不也是你的人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.78,0:17:32.53,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an9}是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:08.85,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你在開玩笑嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.45,0:18:19.20,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8}最後一擊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:40.14,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an9}胡說！ 攻進這個星球的你們會和我們一起攻打地球？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:34.27,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an9}攘夷志士？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.19,0:19:34.27,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}調查報告裡沒提到他們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:36.11,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}立刻前去支援
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.07,0:19:38.49,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an8}讓他們全部化為宇宙的塵埃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.24,0:19:42.07,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an9}閣…閣下{\fscx200}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:42.07,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}後…後面!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:51.04,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an9}那是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.96,0:19:51.04,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什…什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:01.05,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an6}在笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.33,0:20:29.33,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是…這是!!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:29.33,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an5\pos(430,198)}閣…閣下{\fscx200}!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:21.42,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an9}看來混進來的不只是老鼠啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:33.18,Banner2b,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\an9}你算計我

